:::


#### Top 10 repos by stars

Below is a "Top 10 repos by stars" bar graph using `stargazers_count` and `repo`:


::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="false"}
stats$stars |>
  head(10) |>
  ggplot(aes(
    x = stargazers_count,
    y = reorder(repo, stargazers_count)
  )) +
  geom_col(fill = "#1E5F8C") +
  labs(
    x = "Stars",
    y = NULL,
    title = "Top 10 repos by stars"
  ) +
  theme_minimal()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/top-10-repos-by-stars-1.png){fig-align='center' width=100%}
:::
:::


